## ğŸ”¥ 4.4. Konfigurace pÅ™esmÄ›rovÃ¡nÃ­ portu a/nebo firewall

SpecifickÃ© pro nastavenÃ­ sÃ­tÄ› nebo nastavenÃ­ poskytovatele cloudu, [ujistÄ›te se, Å¾e porty vaÅ¡eho validÃ¡tora firewallu jsou otevÅ™enÃ© a dosaÅ¾itelnÃ©.](guide-or-security-best-practices-for-a-eth2-validator-beaconchain-node.md#configure-your-firewall)

* **Lighthouse beacon chain** requires port 9000 for tcp and udp
* **eth1** uzel vyÅ¾aduje port 30303 pro tcp a udp

{% hint style="info" %}
âœ¨ **Tip:** Budete muset pÅ™eposÃ­lat a otevÅ™Ã­t porty vaÅ¡emu ovÄ›Å™ovateli. OvÄ›Å™te, zda pracuje s [https://www.yougetsignal.com/tools/open-ports/](https://www.yougetsignal.com/tools/open-ports/) nebo [https://canyouseeme.org/](https://canyouseeme.org/).
