* **Nimbus beacon chain node** will use port 9000 for tcp and udp
* **eth1** uzel vyÅ¾aduje port 30303 pro tcp a udp

{% hint style="info" %}
âœ¨ **Tip:** Budete muset pÅ™eposÃ­lat a otevÅ™Ã­t porty vaÅ¡emu ovÄ›Å™ovateli. OvÄ›Å™te, zda pracuje s [https://www.yougetsignal.com/tools/open-ports/](https://www.yougetsignal.com/tools/open-ports/) nebo [https://canyouseeme.org/](https://canyouseeme.org/).
{% endhint %}

