#### ğŸš€ Setup Graffiti and POAP

Setup your `graffiti`, a custom message included in blocks your validator successfully proposes, and earn a POAP token. [Generate your POAP string by supplying an Ethereum 1.0 address here.](https://beaconcha.in/poap)

Run the following command to set the `MY_GRAFFITI` variable. Replace `<my POAP string or message>` between the single quotes.

```bash
MY_GRAFFITI='<my POAP string or message>'
# Examples
# MY_GRAFFITI='poapAAAAACGatUA1bLuDnL4FMD13BfoD'
# MY_GRAFFITI='eth2 rulez!'
```

{% hint style="info" %}
Learn more about [POAP - The Proof of Attendance token. ](https://www.poap.xyz/)
{% endhint %}

Volba validÃ¡tora ruÄnÄ› z pÅ™Ã­kazovÃ© Å™Ã¡dky nebo automaticky se systÃ©mem.

#### ğŸ° VÃ½hody z pouÅ¾Ã­vÃ¡nÃ­ systÃ©mu pro vaÅ¡eho validÃ¡tora <a id="benefits-of-using-systemd-for-your-stake-pool"></a>

1. Automaticky spustit validÃ¡tor, kdyÅ¾ poÄÃ­taÄ restartuje kvÅ¯li ÃºdrÅ¾bÄ›, vÃ½padku napÃ¡jenÃ­ atd.
2. Automaticky restartovat procesy validÃ¡tora.
3. Maximalizujte Äas a vÃ½kon svÃ©ho ovÄ›Å™ovatele.

#### ğŸ›  Setup Instructions for systemd

SpusÅ¥te nÃ¡sledujÃ­cÃ­ pro vytvoÅ™enÃ­ **souboru jednotek** pro definovÃ¡nÃ­ konfigurace`validator.service`. Simply copy and paste.

```bash
