* **Lodestar beacon chain node** will use port 30607 for tcp and port 9000 for udp peer discovery.
* **eth1** uzel vyÅ¾aduje port 30303 pro tcp a udp

{% hint style="info" %}
\*\*\*\*âœ¨ **Port Forwarding Tip:** You'll need to forward and open ports to your validator. OvÄ›Å™te, zda pracuje s [https://www.yougetsignal.com/tools/open-ports/](https://www.yougetsignal.com/tools/open-ports/) nebo [https://canyouseeme.org/](https://canyouseeme.org/).
{% endhint %}

