SpusÅ¥te nÃ¡sledujÃ­cÃ­ pro zapnutÃ­ automatickÃ©ho startu pÅ™i startu a pak spusÅ¥te svÅ¯j validÃ¡tor.

```text
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl aktivuje validÃ¡tor
sudo systemctl start validator
```

{% hint style="success" %}
DobrÃ¡ prÃ¡ce. Your validator is now managed by the reliability and robustness of systemd. NÃ­Å¾e jsou nÄ›kterÃ© pÅ™Ã­kazy pro pouÅ¾itÃ­ systÃ©mu.
{% endhint %}

### ğŸ›  NÄ›kterÃ© nÃ¡pomocnÃ© systÃ©movÃ© pÅ™Ã­kazy

#### âœ… Zkontrolujte, zda je validÃ¡tor aktivnÃ­

```text
